{
  "stem": "16571.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 297.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So who knows?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I might have had 1,000 people working for me, or been a-- a-- a tailor instead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that-- that this part of my story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But what happened, about five, six years ago, my brother took his two strappy sons to Romania to show them where we were born.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they came home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unbeknown to him, they had a jar and they filled it with ashes, and they didn't tell him till they got back to Israel what they'd done.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that-- My brother went to the [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "RAF ?] in [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rehovot-- ?] because my brother lives [INAUDIBLE] here, and told him what happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they wanted-- they asked whether he could have a [NON-ENGLISH] for our parents, and my brother, and sister whom we lost.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "RAF ?] gave his permission.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we all paid so much towards a [NON-ENGLISH], and I went with my wife to Israel, and we had a stone setting.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was about 50-plus people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I feel that this is a very good thing, what we've done, because every time I go to Israel, I go to the-- visit the holy grounds, and I say, Kaddish and-- when I get there for-- and then when-- before I leave.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And also this stone setting was all-- all in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't touch me at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't understand what it was all about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went back a few days later with my sister-in-law, and my wife and my brother, and I said to him, now explain to me in English, what does it mean?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when she explained word-for-word, four-- all four of us cried our eyes out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For 15 minutes, I was sobbing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could not stop.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
